      </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Psychology              : The course focuses on the social psychology of societal groups such as racial minorities, aboriginal groups and women. The ideological biases of current theories is first established. This is followed by a review of current theories and finally current controversies are explored including new forms of racism and affirmative action.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
